地冇錯 認同<span style=\"color: red;\">民主黨</span>今次有問題 <br />\n但係今時今日 追住佢地咬好無謂 <br />\n係咁多"},{"pid":"6ec3866ac297ad8b07e2f102b919c3e0ae4a28d2","tid":21978,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"是先有世风日下<br />\n还是先有道德沦丧"},{"pid":"914eedfd6dd3298293107cf884d5d4fa485c0c70","tid":21978,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算吧啦 依條冇野撈等死既廢老</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n答唔撚到就直接話人廢老，垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n短評：<br />\n1.以上市為例，保薦人既責任只限於due diligence,proper disclosure.梁生事前冇話用身家性命擔保，事後亦無責任咁做。仲話歐洲都係咁，吹得就吹，係咁既投行既人起碼一半俾人誅撚左9族<br />\n<br />\n2. 梁天琦話plan b 代替佢既政治理念（99%相同）做野，事後佢地都係行佢既路線。青政能力唔好大家知，梁，青政亦冇作大，選前間接直接認左多次。現在青政失敗，等如上市公司生意失敗，係有proper disclosure,冇fraud 情況下，保薦人係冇責任。<br />\n<br />\n3.紅字大都係誅心論，陳雲假設佢係梁生條蟲，不值一提"},{"pid":"0de6784233102af658b7ba0a4d195d258c1ebfd7","tid":21978,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是先有世风日下<br />\n还是先有道德沦丧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打殘體死番支那啦"},{"pid":"be1f69318bc55356d39fdae0705cf30955069faf","tid":21978,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>算吧啦 依條冇野撈等死既廢老</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n答唔撚到就直接話人廢老，垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢老網上9up 下帶起到本土思潮<br />\n廢老寫得出城邦治國論 仲要俾外國拎黎用 港豬都唔識貨<br />\n呢條廢老真係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本土思潮從來唔係佢帶起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uploa